OL,5, The UK's bottle deposit and return     
OL,6, scheme (DRS) will be delayed until     
OL,7, 2027, four years later than planned.   
OL,9,FMinisters blamed the Welsh government  
OL,10,Ffor wanting to include glass in the    
OL,11,Fscheme - which the UK government       
OL,12,Fopposes.                               
OL,14,FCharities said the delay "makes a      
OL,15,Fmockery" of the government's           
OL,16,Fenvironmental commitments.             
OL,18,FThe beleaguered scheme would reward    
OL,19,Fconsumers recycling bottles with money 
OL,20,For vouchers.                           
